metadata.name: Château entouré d'eau
metadata.description:
Inspired by castles along the river Loire in France.
This piece represents a creative way to make a home inside a refurbished old castle.
The Chenonceau castle left an architectural inprint as well as the feeling of protection each of them creates.

This piece is one of it`s kind - Given out in HD 2048 x 2048 pxls.
Part of a limited series of 10 creative homes.
